ZH: 富人通常住在富裕的社区里。
EN: Rich people usually live in affluent communities.

ZH: 很多富人拥有私人飞机。
EN: Many rich people own private jets.

ZH: 富人喜欢购买奢侈品。
EN: Rich people like to buy luxury goods.

ZH: 富人有的时候会对穷人不友善。
EN: Rich people can sometimes be unkind to the poor.

ZH: 一些富人选择慈善事业来回馈社会。
EN: Some rich people choose to give back to society through charitable activities.

ZH: 富人的生活方式通常很奢华。
EN: Rich people's lifestyles are usually very luxurious.

ZH: 富人花大量的钱在名牌服装上。
EN: Rich people spend a lot of money on designer clothes.

ZH: 富人经常在高级酒店住宿。
EN: Rich people often stay in luxury hotels.

ZH: 即使是富人也有他们自己的烦恼。
EN: Even rich people have their own troubles.

ZH: 富人有时会在世界各地旅行。
EN: Rich people sometimes travel around the world.

ZH: 富人可以在高档餐厅享受美食。
EN: Rich people can enjoy gourmet food in upscale restaurants.

ZH: 富人经常举办豪华的派对。
EN: Rich people often throw extravagant parties.

ZH: 富人拥有私人游艇和豪华轿车。
EN: Rich people own private yachts and luxury cars.

ZH: 富人的孩子上的是昂贵的私立学校。
EN: Rich people's children attend expensive private schools.

ZH: 富人有时会投资在股票市场。
EN: Rich people sometimes invest in the stock market.

ZH: 富人拥有巨额财富。
EN: Rich people have enormous wealth.

ZH: 富人往往对金钱的价值有不同的看法。
EN: Rich people often have different perspectives on the value of money.

ZH: 富人在各行各业都有充足的代表。
EN: Rich people are well-represented in various industries.

ZH: 富人通常在高级社交圈中交往。
EN: Rich people usually socialize in exclusive circles.
